        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "To unify the two sums, we substitute in the first case x = 2u +1,y = 2v +1,z = 2w + 1 and in the second case x = 2u +2, y = 2v +2,z = 2w + 2 to obtain",
